description: Reserved matters submission relating to design, external appearance & landscaping for Phase 2 of the planning permission (Ref:06/1751/O approved 27/07/2007) comprising 297 residential units, large retail store (A1-Tesco)other retail or food & drink units (use classes A1,A2,A3,A4,A5) and neighbourhood police office (D1)together with association public realm, pedestrian & vehicular access, car & cycle parking servicing landscaping highway & other works.
